<div class="container content is-large is-fluid has-text-justified">
  <div class="has-text-centered mb-6">
    <h1 class="title is-1 has-text-centered is-slightblack my-6">
      INNOSERV
    </h1>
    <h2 class="subtitle is-2 has-text-centered is-color-primary mt-3">
      <%= 'Social Services Innovation'.upcase %>
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div class="content has-text-justified">
    <p class="subtitle is-4 mt-3 has-text-weight-semibold">
    INNOSERV is a project developing an EU wide research agenda to evaluate innovation in the field of social
    services (especially for health, education and welfare services). 
    This will help define future research activities.
    </p>
    <p class="is-size-5">
      INNOSERV responds to the FP7-Cooperation call FP7-SSH-2011-3 for a ‘support action concerning a social platform on innovative social services.’
      Answering the objectives of the call, the INNOSERV project will:
    </p>
    <ul class="is-size-5">
      <li>Produce short visual examples combined with theoretical case studies of ‘innovative’ practices in the fields of health, education and welfare. These will be used to help inform discussion and debate;</li>
      <li>Develop a web based ‘social platform’ for continuing dialogue;</li>
      <li>Manage a multi-level discussion involving a wide range of stakeholders from research, policy making and practice communities in the EU to identify priorities for future research and development.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="has-text-centered">
    <%= button_to "Learn More", 
        about_path,
        method: :get,
        class: "button is-uppercase has-text-weight-bold is-background-color-primary is-medium is-centered is-outlined" 
    %>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="trailer" class="is-background-color-primary has-text-centered <%= request.variant.include?(:phone) ? 'py-3 px-2' : 'p-6' %>">
  <h2 class="title is-2 has-text-centered has-text-light my-6">
    INNOSERV Video Trailer
  </h2>
  <figure class="image is-16by9 <%= request.variant.include?(:phone) ? '' : 'm-6' %>">
    <%= video_tag "/videos/Trailer INNOSERV.mp4", class:"is-centered has-ratio", poster: 'Trailer-INNOSERV.webp', controls: true, preload: 'none'%>
  </figure>
</div>


